      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GEORGE ALEXIS (3) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and four placings from nine starts. Hit the frame latest (23.66) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. Rates on top and should go close. MISS SENORITA (2) jumped cleanly from the rails last start to lead all the way and score (23.70) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 407m. Can make it two on the bounce. HENNESSY GOLD (6) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Bandit Chloe (23.99) in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to be in the finish again. AGRARI BEACH (1) placed last start at big odds and is in the mix again.",
